1. *Pre* nego što odemo, želim da prošetamo do parka. (Before we go, I want to take a walk to the park.)

2. *Pre* par dana mogla sam da vidim taj zaboravljeni grad. (A few days ago I was able to see that forgotten town.)

3. On je znao da se zaštiti *pre* nego što je počeo da radi tu posao. (He knew how to protect himself before he started that job.)

4. Svi smo mogli da vidimo da je uspeo da se izbori *pre* nego što je stigao na cilj. (We all could see that he had succeeded before he reached the goal.)

5. Ona je prethodno radila tu posao *pre* nego što je došla u ovu firmu. (She had previously done that job before she came to this company.)